{
  "texts": [
    "The above two junior radiologists were also invited to manually calculate the CTR of each CXR according to the clinical measurement rules, and their average values were considered as the reference standards.",
    "If both radiologists were unable to calculate the CTR, the corresponding CXR was excluded.",
    "If only one junior radiologist could not calculate it or the difference between the CTR results measured by two junior radiologists was greater than 0.05, the above senior radiologist was invited to achieve a final consensus result.",
    "Ultimately, 1950 CXRs were included when constructing a test dataset.",
    "In addition, 500 CXRs randomly selected from each hospital were used for multicentre validation, and 300 randomly selected CXRs were used for prospective validation."
  ]
}